---
import "../../global.css";
---

<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Chatbot WhatsApp - Case Study</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-neutral-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-8"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_back</span>
          Voltar
        </a>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/40 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
              Chatbot WhatsApp
            </h1>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg">
              Sistema Inteligente de Atendimento ao Cliente com IA
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase">Status</p>
              <p class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Em Produção</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase">Timeline</p>
              <p class="font-semibold">2024 - Presente</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase">Clientes</p>
              <p class="font-semibold">2+ empresas</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase">Meu Papel</p>
              <p class="font-semibold">Full-Stack Dev</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- O Problema -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">🤔 O Problema</h2>
        <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-neutral-300">
            Empresas recebem centenas de mensagens diárias no WhatsApp, mas 
            atender manualmente consome muito tempo e recursos. O desafio era 
            automatizar respostas mantendo a qualidade do atendimento.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-500">•</span>
              <span>Respostas lentas causam perda de clientes (drop de 40%)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-500">•</span>
              <span>Equipe gasta 6+ horas por dia respondendo dúvidas repetitivas</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-500">•</span>
              <span>Leads interessados saem sem acompanhamento</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-500">•</span>
              <span>Sem dados sobre quais dúvidas são mais frequentes</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Solução -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">✨ A Solução</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Como Funciona</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300 list-decimal list-inside">
              <li>Mensagem chega no WhatsApp</li>
              <li>Webhook dispara para nosso backend</li>
              <li>OpenAI API processa e entende a intenção</li>
              <li>Sistema responde automaticamente ou escala para atendente</li>
              <li>Lead é classificado e adicionado ao CRM</li>
              <li>Dados alimentam dashboard de análise</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Arquitetura Técnica</h3>
            <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm space-y-2 font-mono">
              <p><span class="text-blue-400">WhatsApp API</span> → Webhook → <span class="text-green-400">Express.js</span></p>
              <p><span class="text-green-400">Express.js</span> → <span class="text-purple-400">OpenAI</span> (entender intenção)</p>
              <p><span class="text-green-400">Express.js</span> → <span class="text-orange-400">Supabase</span> (armazenar conversa)</p>
              <p><span class="text-green-400">Express.js</span> → <span class="text-red-400">CRM Integration</span> (classificar lead)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Capacidades Principais</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-2">🤖 NLU - Entender Intenção</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
                  "Qual é o preço?" → Intenção: PRICING | 
                  "Como faço brinde?" → Intenção: HELP
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-2">📊 Classificação de Leads</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
                  HOT: Pronto para comprar | WARM: Interessado | 
                  COLD: Apenas explorador
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-2">⚡ Escalação Inteligente</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
                  Se o bot não tem resposta, escalona para atendente 
                  mantendo histórico
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-2">📈 Analytics Real-Time</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
                  Dashboard mostra: mensagens/dia, taxa de conversão, 
                  tópicos mais comuns
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Stack Técnico -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">build</span> Stack Técnico</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase mb-3">Backend</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">Express.js</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">TypeScript</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">Node.js</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase mb-3">IA & Integrações</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-purple-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">OpenAI GPT-4</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-purple-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">WhatsApp API</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-purple-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">Webhooks</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs uppercase mb-3">Data & Storage</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">Supabase</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange-400">→</span>
                <span class="text-sm">Redis Cache</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Resultados -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">📊 Resultados em Produção</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-emerald-700/20 border border-emerald-700/40 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-emerald-400 text-3xl font-bold">95%</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Mensagens respondidas automaticamente</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-emerald-700/20 border border-emerald-700/40 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-emerald-400 text-3xl font-bold">2min</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Tempo médio de resposta (vs 30min antes)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-emerald-700/20 border border-emerald-700/40 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-emerald-400 text-3xl font-bold">40%</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Aumento em leads captados</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-emerald-700/20 border border-emerald-700/40 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-emerald-400 text-3xl font-bold">85%</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-2">Economia de tempo da equipe</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Desafios & Soluções -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">🔧 Desafios Superados</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">⚠</span> Latência de Resposta
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mb-2">
              <strong>Problema:</strong> OpenAI API leva 2-3s para responder
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
              <strong>Solução:</strong> Implementar cache Redis para respostas comuns, 
              processamento assíncrono, pre-compute de respostas
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">⚠</span> Context Window
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mb-2">
              <strong>Problema:</strong> Manter histórico de conversa sem exceder limite de tokens
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
              <strong>Solução:</strong> Implementar sliding window, resumir conversas antigas, 
              armazenar em PostgreSQL
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-700/20 border border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">⚠</span> Custos de API
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mb-2">
              <strong>Problema:</strong> Cada chamada custa dinheiro, volume crescente = custos crescentes
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">
              <strong>Solução:</strong> Modelo de negócio: cobrar por mensagem, implementar rate limiting, 
              priorizar clientes
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="border-t border-neutral-700 pt-8 mt-12">
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
          Desenvolvido como parte da estratégia de automação de vendas da NovusTech.
          <a href="/" class="text-white hover:underline ml-1">Voltar ao portfólio</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
